# The SecPrax Podcast Generator

Turn any content into engaging audio podcasts with AI-powered script generation and multi-voice narration.

## Features

- üåê **Multiple Input Methods**
  - Scrape webpages
  - Upload files (PDF, DOC, DOCX, XLS, XLSX, PPT, PPTX)
  - Paste text directly

- üéôÔ∏è **AI Script Generation**
  - 4 podcast styles: Two-Host Conversation, Solo Narrator, Interview, Storytelling
  - 2 length options: Short (3-5 min), Longer (8-12 min)
  - Powered by Claude AI (Sonnet 4)

- üé¨ **Professional Audio Production**
  - Multi-voice narration with ElevenLabs
  - Custom voices: Lily & Simon
  - Automatic stage direction removal
  - Download as MP3

- ‚úèÔ∏è **Full Editing Control**
  - Edit generated scripts before conversion
  - Paste your own pre-written scripts
  - Manual script customization

